description: Triangle T(n,k) giving number of pairwise non-isomorphic (i.e., unlabeled) matroids of rank k on n points (n >= 0, 0<=k<=n).

Dillon Mayhew and Gordon F. Royle, Matroids with nine elements, arXiv:math/0702316 [math.CO], 2007 (see p. 7).
